Rules.InvariantScript: "Input details below to create new organization record "

UpdateContext({visibleOrg:false});
If(
    IsBlank(DataCardValue6.Text),Notify("You must enter an Organization Name", NotificationType.Error),
   If(IsBlank(City_3.Selected), Notify("You must choose a City", NotificationType.Error),
  If(IsBlank(Dropdown1.Selected), Notify("You must choose a UWBC Region", NotificationType.Error),


Collect(Organization,{City:City_3.SelectedText.Value, 
'Organization Name':DataCardValue6.Text, 
'Postal Code':DataCardValue7.Text,
AndarID:DataCardValue5.Text,
UWBCRegionID:Dropdown1.SelectedText.Value,
ID:IdTxt2.Text});
ResetForm(OrgForm_Input);
Navigate('Organization Form Input', ScreenTransition.Fade)
)))
